# WalletConnect Cloud project id (https://cloud.walletconnect.com).
# Enables the WalletConnect connector in the widget's standalone mode.
# Without it, only the injected (browser-wallet) connector is offered.
#
# Standalone + WalletConnect also requires (already set up here):
#   - the `@walletconnect/ethereum-provider` dependency (wagmi's optional peer), and
#   - Node global polyfills in the bundler (see vite-plugin-node-polyfills in vite.config.ts).
VITE_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID=
